Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.63,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}Konna itami mo kangei jan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.12,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.33,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you remember it from that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:44.25,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We made a promise and a vow while the early summer wind circled us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.51,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}And we clung close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:57.56,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Your forced smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:02.94,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Holds elongated shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:12.20,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}I pretend not to notice and continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:21.71,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}All the while waiting for you to deliver some news at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:30.09,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Empty nights, mornings that will never arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:34.85,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I could see them from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:40.48,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:45.40,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm sure you'll remember it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:51.24,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}While holding the promise we couldn't keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:55.49,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}We take our first steps down our own paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.12,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)}{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.33,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　君は覚えていますか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:44.25,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}約束　契り　初夏の風が包む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.51,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　寄り添った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:57.56,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}無理な笑顔の裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:02.94,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伸びた影をかくまう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:12.20,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}だから　気づかぬふり　再生を選ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:21.71,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}テーブルの上の　震えない知らせ　待ち続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:30.09,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}空白の夜も　来るはずのない朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:34.85,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全部わかってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:40.48,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:45.40,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　 いつか思い出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:51.24,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果たせなかった　約束を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:55.49,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.12,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Ano hi mita sora akaneiro no sora wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.33,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nee kimi wa oboeteimasuka
