Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.02,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is a science where one understands the structure of matter, breaks it down, then rebuilds it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:11.61,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is not an all-powerful technique,\Nas one cannot create something out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.66,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to gain something,\None must present something of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:22.16,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,This is the concept of equivalent exchange, the fundamental basis of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.79,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a taboo in alchemy. Human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.46,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,One must not commit this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:09.06,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Marcoh, the man who Ed and Al met, possessed\Na Philosopher's Stone, although it was incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:15.73,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Moved by Ed's passion, Marcoh revealed the location his research data was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:25.99,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,And so, after having his automail repaired,\NEd stood before the place Marcoh's data was located...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.87,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,National Central Library, 1st Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:36.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh's research data!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.30,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,It was too much effort to look for it,\Nso I just burnt down the whole building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.10,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do at Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.60,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I've been explaining to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.98,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,The Fullmetal boy found out about Marcoh's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:56.44,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,After I took care of that, I came back to East City to check on things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.82,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.70,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.41,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell... I can smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.95,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,There's an Ishbalan nearby that smells like blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.71,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.04,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but eat every bit of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:55.46,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,There have been no sightings of Scar\Nsince the case involving the Elric brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.84,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not in East City anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I need him to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.26,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:07.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I can solve the case that was left unresolved in Central, it should raise my status in the public's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.64,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take advantage of everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:18.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Until I become the Führer and gain full authority over the military, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.28,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to refrain from making inappropriate remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.45,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.75,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a report of an explosion by Merle River!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A gas explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.17,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so unsafe lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.51,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs to Scar. There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Have any bodies been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.39,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,We've been searching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.73,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, judging from this blood, it is safe to assume that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But still, we cannot let our guard down until we confirm his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.69,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.19,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:06.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your squad is to clear all of the rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no breaks, whether it be for lunch or supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Drag his body out, no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.79,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.62,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:21.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even calm myself for a date until I see his dead body with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.21,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.47,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.97,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to eat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.47,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:35.31,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he probably won't be able to do anything for a while after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.94,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Central again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.11,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I need to report to Father about Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's been burnt to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.16,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:56.41,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, 2nd Lt. Ross and Sergeant Brosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.50,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.75,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,We've received orders from Headquarters to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:04.59,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,We will take over the escort of Sir Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.63,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,All right, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:12.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! Just when I thought I'd get rid of this smothering guy for good, I get more escorts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:19.69,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone well-versed in the data that was in the Library's 1st Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.40,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Although she is no longer employed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I shouldn't expect much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.61,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.08,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my impudence, but why are you wearing a suit of armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.87,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Just a hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.29,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,"Hobby"? Second Lieutenant, what kind of hobby is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.62,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with these kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Al, the scenery is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:55.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these mountains of books?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.52,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really someone living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.19,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sheska, are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.65,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sheska!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.15,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.15,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:12.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is buried under the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dig! Dig! Dig! Dig over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:18.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.58,Default-alt,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.84,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.05,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly knocked over a mountain of books...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.22,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was the end for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.80,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Sheska?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.10,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was at the 1st Branch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.93,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,1st Branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.23,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, even the name gives off a sweet sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:49.69,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved books ever since I was born, and I felt like I was being sent to Heaven when I got a job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:55.82,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,But I forgot that I was at work and was fired because I was reading all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:01.91,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I need a job to send\Nmy sick mother to a better hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:09.63,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I've got no skills besides reading, and I can't find a job no matter where I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:13.84,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm a failure! I'm the trash of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.14,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I've got something I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.43,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:21.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know of any\Nresearch documents by Tim Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.64,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Tim Marcoh... Tim Marcoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.81,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yes, I do remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:32.69,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it clearly because it was handwritten and shoved into a shelf in the wrong section.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So it really was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...which means that it's ashes now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.25,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to read the research?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's gone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.67,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything in it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.67,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:57.30,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I remember the content of every book that I've ever read.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.31,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a while, but would you like me to transcribe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, bookworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.94,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,...Worm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.81,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the duplicate of Mr. Tim Marcoh's research!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:15.20,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it took five days because there was just so much to write down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:19.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There really are amazing people in this world, aren't there, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really Dr. Marcoh's research?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.08,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.50,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,"1000 Meals for Daily Living", written by Tim Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.42,Default,Every,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.59,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,"Add a bit of water to a tablespoon of sugar"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.05,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,These really are 1000 meals for daily living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.09,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What part this makes it an important document?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:42.22,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,But... all I did was copy things down exactly as I'd remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.14,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we just went on a wild goose chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:49.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is word for word what Dr. Marcoh wrote, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.44,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's take this back to the Central Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They've got a lot of related books there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:03.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. I need to reward you for all that work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:13.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lt. Ross, this is my registration code\Nand silver pocket watch as ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw the amount written on there from\Nmy annual research expenditures and give it to Sheska.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:23.97,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so I just have to go to the state alchemist facility at the Führer administrative building, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again, Sheska!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:28.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.98,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so from his research expenditures...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.90,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this number?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.74,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,He can just pull out a sum like this as if it's nothing?! What is that boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:49.29,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Are these recipes really research documents for alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:53.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is dangerous when abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent that, alchemists encrypt their research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:04.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx98}An ordinary person may think it's just a cooking experiment; only the one who wrote it will understand the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's an advanced alchemy document.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.69,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to decipher it\Nif only the author can understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledge and inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of it will all be busy work with patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.19,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this'll take a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, there's something about a pigeon dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Pigeon? Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It could be about the Green Lion. The philosopher's moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:33.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring Flamel's manuscripts\Nor books on Lambspring's philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Hey, look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This has to do with it, too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right! This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:45.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. All right, let's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:59.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this encryption hard as hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'll be faster to just ask Dr. Marcoh himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No! If we ask him, we lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:08.99,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sheska.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:19.05,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to transfer my mother to a wonderful hospital thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.59,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.80,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Any progress on the decoding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:38.06,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you two, I realized that even a failure like me can be useful to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.07,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a failure at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:47.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I believe being able to wholeheartedly commit yourself to something is a talent in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,and you have an amazing memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You should have more confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.66,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.00,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Colonel Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.92,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Major Armstrong you guys were back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.64,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... I told you guys to come\Nsay hi when you stopped by Central again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I had urgent matters to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.39,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've been kind of busy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.31,Default-alt,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,He's chatting to Lt. Colonel Hughes like they're buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.19,Default-alt,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,What are those boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.48,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of incidents and such lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.69,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,The case with Tucker and the chimera hasn't been solved yet, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.78,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.03,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I made you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.95,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:35.33,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,It's busy enough, and the 1st Branch of the library just had to burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The 1st Branch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:43.46,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We kept a lot of case records and whatnot in the archives, so it really messes with our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.97,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Lt. Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.56,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have read army criminal records and remember them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.86,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's get you set up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.36,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,We pay really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.65,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,That's... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.49,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.49,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have more confidence in myself, and I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.28,Default,Sch,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.24,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I need you to get to work right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, a kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:26.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"I believe being able to wholeheartedly commit yourself to something is a talent in itself", huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wise words, little bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:34.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I really feel that way, especially when I look at a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:42.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then that certain someone's going to keep working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.63,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.59,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.31,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten days already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.60,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they have the fortitude\Nto work every day until this place closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.07,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Sibling fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.16,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get desperate simply because you can't solve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We did solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We solved the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.25,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no, it's not great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"The Devil's research"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Something you mustn't desire"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I resent you, Dr. Marcoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.38,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,What... exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients of philosopher's stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...are live humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:04.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, you need several sacrifices just to refine one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:08.15,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never thought something so inhumane was going on in the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.98,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,That's something that can't be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please not tell anyone about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.12,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.38,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.80,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric brothers have locked themselves in their room again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.13,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They haven't eaten much, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.89,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they were really tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.98,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Seems they've been working extremely hard these past days, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.31,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if {\i1}that's{\i0\fscx30} {\r} what they found after all of that difficult deciphering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.86,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Even I start feeling sick when I start thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.94,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.61,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.28,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, go get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right when you get within arm's reach, it runs away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:26.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...and when you finally grab it, it kicks you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:32.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,God must really hate humans who have committed taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:39.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be like this for the rest of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... there's something I've always wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've been too scared to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.22,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Elric brothers! You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.14,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.77,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the whole story, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.48,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.86,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,To think that such a horrifying secret laid beneath the philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.45,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,S... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.07,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Not much we could do when such\Na smothering person approaches you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.12,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,To think the army had been doing such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.83,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The truth can be cruel at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember Dr. Marcoh's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.09,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,"You may be able to reach\Nthe real truth that is beyond truth..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The real truth beyond truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Same as a research document for alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What can be seen from the outside is only a portion of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:19:00.45,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,There are currently four alchemy research laboratories owned by the government within Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.99,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The one Dr. Marcoh belonged to is Research Laboratory 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.41,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,This one is the most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:14.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We went around to every research lab in the city,\Nbut this one wasn't particularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This. What's this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.47,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,That would be Research Laboratory 5,\Nbut it's not being used right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.76,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,No one is allowed to enter it due to risk of collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.43,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's a prison right next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.56,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what's needed to create philosopher's stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.86,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... was it live humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There are bound to be people on the death row at the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They tell the public they were executed, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.41,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... the prisoners are the ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think about it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The prison is under a different\Njurisdiction, but if it's involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean the government has something to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:00.88,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've stuck my nose into something horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we asked you to forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:11.23,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,This may turn into a political matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.27,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.56,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,But until then, the 2nd Lt. and\Nthe Sergeant are not to speak of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.52,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.32,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You two better not do anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:28.91,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You two were thinking of sneaking into the building to check it out, weren't you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.83,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't! We weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:43.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A guard at an unused building, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How should we get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How about we just make an entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They'll notice the flash of the transmutation response.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Here we... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This place is completely shut down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:29.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you can't get through here with that big body of yours, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I chose to have a big body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.90,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,66.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.07,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What, 48?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.28,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Our first guest in quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.99,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What a reckless dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is narrower than I'd thought, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I probably wouldn't have been able to get through if I was normal-sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I'm small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:03.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I called myself small!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The lights are on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:12.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Not being used right now my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:18.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother sure is taking his time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:01.12,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man who held pride in his swordsmanship,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.92,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and there was also another man who understood he was a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:09.59,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The residents of darkness jeer, and\Nthe blades that drank blood are shrieking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:14.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8, The Fifth Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:23.60,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ones who seek pleasure in fighting and continue to live forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.52,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...speak thy names.
